I am in, just let me know and make it so I can pay a year at once so I don't have to think about it. I would rather pay a little more and not loose any economically challenged members that do allot more then me. One thought would be to put a guild level that does not pay (second lowest) and the quest is to come up with the real world money to get higher so we could continue to attract new members without having to bill them after joining.  I also respect the time this must take you for nothing more then a thank you..Thank You Tormod<br>
<br>
